&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1306685 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_8400-1-289x580.jpg" alt="" width="289" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_8400-1-289x580.jpg 289w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img_8400-1-scaled.jpg 448w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 289px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
